BioCelegans

The undirected graph BioCelegans has 453 nodes and 2025 edges.

RAM requirements

The RAM requirements for the nodes and edges data structures are 67.29KB and 4.22KB respectively.

Degree centrality

The minimum node degree is 1, the maximum node degree is 237, the mode degree is 3, the mean degree is 8.94 and the node degree median is 5.

The nodes with highest degree centrality are: 1 (degree 237), 18 (degree 123), 11 (degree 109), 17 (degree 104) and 5 (degree 75).
